data.description: Detached Single Ranch Home--Parkland School District!  This 3 bedroom 1 full bath is ready to welcome new owners!  This house has a new kitchen and most floors are new.  Redesigned layout offers an oversized space currently used as family room and dining room with access to the large deck, fenced in yard and detached oversized garage.  The lower level has been updated for many possibilities--let your creativity run free.
